{"tid":1883,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"求教於作曲嘅你，平時係點作曲","createTime":"2016-11-25T17:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T17:37:54.000Z","uid":12415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc203383b6392d3fe6d2dcaa9b1742b3e70dff3d","tid":1883,"uid":12415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"到底係寫chord先定諗melody先？<br />\n到底作pop song如何入手？"},{"pid":"a11a8f00f5df4d1be3068440e0c054b757f1f4bf","tid":1883,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:26:02.000Z","msg":"睇下佢邊類型<br />\n作orchestral 野咪跟chord progression<br />\n作pop 咪先寫melody 再harmonise <br />\n利申 Music major, CASH member"},{"pid":"86de37ff9f48f4945fdf91bad3f7b9c4ca439ce7","tid":1883,"uid":12415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下佢邊類型<br />\n作orchestral 野咪跟chord progression<br />\n作pop 咪先寫melody 再harmonise <br />\n利申 Music major, CASH member</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打真犀利<br />\n<br />\n咁寫pop通常會點配chord？chord progression 通常係點？"},{"pid":"7e7befbd91294f003737afde962405ac08efe9cd","tid":1883,"uid":3904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下佢邊類型<br />\n作orchestral 野咪跟chord progression<br />\n作pop 咪先寫melody 再harmonise <br />\n利申 Music major, CASH member</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打真犀利<br />\n<br />\n咁寫pop通常會點配chord？chord progression 通常係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個有好多方法<br />\n<br />\n最基本做法係要睇你寫果條melody 果個bar入而既重拍係咩音，再配番有果幾個音既chord 落去<br />\n<br />\n或者走circle of fifth 即係 I IV vii III VI ii V I之類<br />\n或者玩下 ii V I progression <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到你樂理有番咁上下就可以學下用啲比較outside嘅chord去撞，例如secondary dominant , tritone substitution 之類"},{"pid":"ac40be93b6794703316086dc95cc77f2b2ab5a87","tid":1883,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"我諗我都可以寫番樂理教學post"},{"pid":"934a9ee3edab8fe9a5d696abfcb9daeb97cc8451","tid":1883,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗我都可以寫番樂理教學post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪識jazz?"},{"pid":"3f5d494777f061d77337e5830b38d7969622bcb1","tid":1883,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗我都可以寫番樂理教學post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪識jazz?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有玩開<br />\n同埋其實我而家有開rockschool grade 8 theory 班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373e65670e1027ca741af1ba4fba0ddd7758c0b9","tid":1883,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗我都可以寫番樂理教學post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪識jazz?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有玩開<br />\n同埋其實我而家有開rockschool grade 8 theory 班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下jazz d樂理同玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e1dc9215ffcb86ebf8450d956abd9f22d24e59","tid":1883,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我諗我都可以寫番樂理教學post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪識jazz?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有玩開<br />\n同埋其實我而家有開rockschool grade 8 theory 班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以教下jazz d樂理同玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最基本要練左jazz入面比較常用嘅mode先，如mixolydian, Dorian, 仲有major/minor blues scale等<br />\n之後就要去理解一首歌chord chart 嘅chord progression <br />\n你會發覺好多都係ii V I <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(打下打下發覺會係幾萬字長文，我都係聽日起身先開教學post）"},{"pid":"0118cc90003d8b2140e85a9c82bc9a4c986f546f","tid":1883,"uid